<dd><cite style="font-style:normal" class="book" id="CITEREF.3Cspan_style.3D.22font-variant:small-caps.3B.22.3EWilcox.2C_David_R..3C.2Fspan.3E1991"><span style="font-variant:small-caps;">Wilcox, David R.</span> (1991). "The Mesoamerican Ballgame in the American Southwest". in Vernon Scarborough and David R. Wilcox (eds.). <i>The Mesoamerican Ballgame</i>. Tucson: <a href="/wiki/University_of_Arizona_Press" title="University of Arizona Press">University of Arizona Press</a>. pp.&#160;101–125. <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/0816511802" class="internal">ISBN 0-8165-1180-2</a>. <a href="/wiki/Online_Computer_Library_Center" title="Online Computer Library Center">OCLC</a> <a href="http://worldcat.org/oclc/22765562" class="external text" title="http://worldcat.org/oclc/22765562" rel="nofollow">22765562</a>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=bookitem&amp;rft.btitle=The+Mesoamerican+Ballgame+in+the+American+Southwest&amp;rft.atitle=The+Mesoamerican+Ballgame&amp;rft.aulast=%3Cspan+style%3D%22font-variant%3Asmall-caps%3B%22%3EWilcox%2C+David+R.%3C%2Fspan%3E&amp;rft.au=%3Cspan+style%3D%22font-variant%3Asmall-caps%3B%22%3EWilcox%2C+David+R.%3C%2Fspan%3E&amp;rft.date=1991&amp;rft.pages=pp.%26nbsp%3B101%E2%80%93125&amp;rft.place=Tucson&amp;rft.pub=%5B%5BUniversity+of+Arizona+Press%5D%5D&amp;rft_id=info:oclcnum/22765562&amp;rft.isbn=0-8165-1180-2&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Mesoamerican_ballgame"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></dd>
<dd><cite style="font-style:normal" class="book" id="CITEREF.3Cspan_style.3D.22font-variant:small-caps.3B.22.3EWilkerson.2C_S._Jeffrey_K..3C.2Fspan.3E1991"><span style="font-variant:small-caps;">Wilkerson, S. Jeffrey K.</span> (1991). "Then They Were Sacrificed: The Ritual Ballgame of Northeastern Mesoamerica Through Time and Space". in Vernon Scarborough and David R. Wilcox (eds.). <i>The Mesoamerican Ballgame</i>. Tucson: <a href="/wiki/University_of_Arizona_Press" title="University of Arizona Press">University of Arizona Press</a>. <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/0816511802" class="internal">ISBN 0-8165-1180-2</a>. <a href="/wiki/Online_Computer_Library_Center" title="Online Computer Library Center">OCLC</a> <a href="http://worldcat.org/oclc/22765562" class="external text" title="http://worldcat.org/oclc/22765562" rel="nofollow">22765562</a>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=bookitem&amp;rft.btitle=Then+They+Were+Sacrificed%3A+The+Ritual+Ballgame+of+Northeastern+Mesoamerica+Through+Time+and+Space&amp;rft.atitle=The+Mesoamerican+Ballgame&amp;rft.aulast=%3Cspan+style%3D%22font-variant%3Asmall-caps%3B%22%3EWilkerson%2C+S.+Jeffrey+K.%3C%2Fspan%3E&amp;rft.au=%3Cspan+style%3D%22font-variant%3Asmall-caps%3B%22%3EWilkerson%2C+S.+Jeffrey+K.%3C%2Fspan%3E&amp;rft.date=1991&amp;rft.place=Tucson&amp;rft.pub=%5B%5BUniversity+of+Arizona+Press%5D%5D&amp;rft_id=info:oclcnum/22765562&amp;rft.isbn=0-8165-1180-2&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Mesoamerican_ballgame"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></dd>
